<p>{{Infobox Occupation}}
<b>Agricultural science</b> is a broad multidisciplinary field that encompasses the parts of exact, natural, economic and <a href="Social_sciences" title="social sciences">social sciences</a> that are used in the practice and understanding of <a href="Agriculture" title="agriculture">agriculture</a>. (<a href="Veterinary_medicine" title="veterinary medicine">Veterinary science</a>, but not <a href="Animal_science" title="animal science">animal science</a>, is often excluded from the definition.)</p>
